Text:
More Stealth Islam?

No seeders anyway....

"Stealth" Islam? Why such paranoia? Moman73 uploads many, many excellent books, including some that are (whether he knows it or not) pro-Christian -- for example, Larry Hurtado in this torrent.

Moman73: keep up the good work.

If you can use the phrase "Stealth Islam" without embarrassment (or irony), then you're a moron.  

moman73, do you have Cambridge History of Christianity, Vol. 3?
